item.title: By: Elizabeth

item.description: Love it! It’s so great to get the mg of nicotine that desire. Cake Stuff tastes great and I will order again! It’s crisp, sweet and clean. Order and delivery were quick and that is very appreciated

item.title: By: rachelklepadlo
item.dc:creator: rachelklepadlo
item.description: This is the flavor that everyone I know has gotten hooked on, and I buy multiple bottles of it a month for everyone - my family, coworkers, and friends. We alter it to add different fruit to it, but it is by far the best base we have ever found.
